PathOfBuilding.Notes:
Weapon - Purchase from trade , or vaal your own.
Quiver - get Fractured crit multi, use torment essence til +1 arrow and open suffix(you can annul) and open prefixes (or non attack prefixes). Craft cannot roll attack mods and Exalt / annul until desired life and increased damage with bows. Craft attack speed.
Body - Get fractured grasping mail mod for lightning. spam int essence til PDR with open suffix . Use suffix cannot change and reforge chaos. You can use eldritch annuls if you get a bad roll. Use eldritch currency to do whatever prefix and craft phys taken as (gravicius mod)
Gloves - Get fractured life. Spam attack speed essence til suppression with open suffix craft aspect of the crab. Use wild bristle for suffix cannot change veiled chaos for Lightning conversion craft damage during flask
Amulet - Buy +1 curse rare jade amulet , use mythic orb pray (1/6)
Ring 1- Get fractured lightning damage to attacks. Spam Multi essence til Str with open suffix. Use suffix cannot change reforge chaos. Use wild bristle matron for suffix cannot change and veiled chaos block mana unveil life. Craft
Ring 2- Get Fractured lighting damage or damage with elemental attack skills and spam multi essence til all res. Use suffix cannot change and reforge chaos. Use wild bristle matron for suffix cannot change and veiled chaos block mana unveil life. Craft
Belt - Do valdos maps with send players to the void if you die for free magebloods
Boots - Get whatever Suppression or Str fracture and spam int essence til one of the other 2. Use wild bristle matron and veiled chaos until movement speed + move speed craft life.
Cluster get ilvl 51-67 cluster and spam crit reforge til martial or calamtious and use exalt for other mod.
